result.execSummary:
The defendant Torrance K Sanders was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Torrance K Sanders is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Torrance K Sanders was found guilty of Battery, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
